.TH wxInitDialogEvent 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxInitDialogEvent \- A \fIwxInitDialogEvent\fR is sent as a dialog or panel is being initialised.

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Handlers for this event can transfer data to the window.

.PP
The default handler calls \fIwxWindow:transferDataToWindow/1\fR.

.PP
See: Overview events

.PP
This class is derived, and can use functions, from:


.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
.\}
.el \{\
.sp -1
.IP \(bu 2.3
.\}.PP
\fIwxEvent\fR

.RE

.PP
wxWidgets docs: wxInitDialogEvent

.SS "Events"

.PP
Use \fIwxEvtHandler:connect/3\fR with \fIwxInitDialogEventType\fR to subscribe to events of this type.

.SH DATA TYPES
.LP
.B
\fBwxInitDialog() :: #wxInitDialog{}.\fR

.br
.RS

.RE
.B
\fBwxInitDialogEvent() :: wx:wx_object().\fR

.br
.RS

.RE
.B
\fBwxInitDialogEventType() :: init_dialog.\fR

.br
.RS

.RE
.SH FUNCTIONS
.LP
